--- HOW TO INSTALL OPENGROK ---
http://hub.opensolaris.org/bin/view/Project+opengrok/installdescription

--- HOW TO INSTALL GEANT4---
cp ~/Downloads/geant4.9.5.p01.tar.gz /tmp
cd /tmp && tar xzfv geant4.9.5.p01.tar.gz
mkdir geant4.9.5.p01-build
cd geant4.9.5.p01-build

sudo yum install cmake
sudo yum groupinstall "X Software Development"		# Needed for visualisation
sudo yum install xerces-c-devel				# Needed for GDML

cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/opt/geant4.9.5.p01	\
      -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug				\
      -DGEANT4_USE_GDML=ON				\
      -DGEANT4_USE_OPENGL_X11=ON			\
            /tmp/geant4.9.5.p01
make -j5
sudo make install

-- HOW TO INSTALL GEANT4 IN SOLARIS 11 ---
* cmake 2.8 is needed, but as of the time of writing, solaris 11 comes with cmake 2.6
* one needs to install cmake 2.6 and use that to bootstrap cmake 2.8
* then user cmake 2.8 to build geant4 as previously

